{"tid":1251180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】金鐘有義士發言，激動人心！","createTime":"2019-06-22T11:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T04:54:52.000Z","uid":14153,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6295835179cfe5aca2a729b46a83a0ff32713d6","tid":1251180,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:55:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZubvzTs9uJ4&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZubvzTs9uJ4%26feature%3Dshare&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3gZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=06f72b0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZubvzTs9uJ4&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n連登仔睇完開頭義士發言有咩感想？<br />\n<br />\n話就話兄弟爬山各自努力，但係一有激烈d既行動建議，就好似條片咁以數量overwhelm人<br />\n<br />\n其實大多數既人，無論咩社會都係咁，西瓜靠大邊，佢地充其量只會遊下行，入下錢俾政黨<br />\n<br />\n再熱心d會企係度包圍現場已經係少數，真正會衝鋒陷陣既係好少數，而佢地先係最有資格點樣行動，因為成本係佢地承受而唔係所謂民意花生友<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講既係，好似條片咁講，革命係要用血同汗付出，唔好太樂觀地認為叫口號同和平就可以取得勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3236f71631cde387fe2cb166c8c0e8eeeb8052fc","tid":1251180,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8fc86341e682e091e2d51070aa8a2a7a3892ea5","tid":1251180,"uid":14153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3236f71631cde387fe2cb166c8c0e8eeeb8052fc","tid":1251180,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"唔配有"},{"pid":"19dd14d4b905e9301b872ff7c723c7eb01fa52c6","tid":1251180,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n早幾日都有聽番<br />\n有d位仲係講得好中"},{"pid":"7dcf2fe94cc3d9df8a13383d6210b1339c3379e4","tid":1251180,"u